#Environment Setup Over Cygwin

1. Install Cmder
2. Install Cygwin
3. Install apt-cyg
4. Install Oh-Myzsh



# Linux Terminal Coding Evironment
## Require:
1. zsh + oh-my-zsh : 
```bash
sh -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)"
wget	
```

2. tmux with .tmux.conf include clipboard copy-paste patch

3. neovim
```bash
curl -LO https://github.com/neovim/neovim/releases/latest/download/nvim.appimage
chmod u+x nvim.appimage
./nvim.appimage
```
4. spacevim
```bash
curl -sLf https://spacevim.org/install.sh | bash -s -- -h
```
spacevim clipboard copy-paste patch
```bash
# configure init.toml for layers
# patch .SpaceVim/config/functions.vim
```
5. nvm
6. phpenv
7. ruby
8. perl
9. pyenv
